00:42:18.235 --> 00:42:20.610
The question was, do you think
citizen science was bigger

00:42:20.610 --> 00:42:23.195
in the 18th century or today?

00:42:23.195 --> 00:42:25.570
Certainly, you can see with
something like the experiment

00:42:25.570 --> 00:42:27.622
of the polyp, it's really easy.

00:42:27.622 --> 00:42:29.580
You go to your local
pond, you pick up a polyp,

00:42:29.580 --> 00:42:31.210
you cut it in two.

00:42:31.210 --> 00:42:33.210
