00:45:57.214 --> 00:45:58.880
SUSANNAH GIBSON: Yeah,
an individual ant

00:45:58.880 --> 00:46:00.600
can't do that well on its own.

00:46:00.600 --> 00:46:03.148
Absolutely.

00:46:03.148 --> 00:46:06.052
FEMALE SPEAKER: I think we have
